Strategies
      Avenue Capital Group's core strategies focus on distressed and undervalued debt and equity opportunities in the U.S., Asia and Europe. In addition, Avenue focuses on real estate and securitized loan obligations. Select an individual strategy to learn more.      * The description of the investment strategies set forth herein are general in nature. 





















