Reflects complaints, answers, motions, orders and trial notes entered from Jan. 1, 2011.Additional or older documents may be available in Pacer.




Coverage


December 13, 2016
Ex-Quiznos Execs Escape Investors' Claims At 10th Circ.
Former Quiznos executives cannot be sued by affiliates of private equity investors Avenue Capital Group LLC and Fortress Investment Group LLC, the Tenth Circuit said Tuesday, finding that the sandwich chain’s 2012 restructuring agreement with the funders didn’t constitute an investment under federal securities law.





